    "body": "I tried with the following code:\n\n``` javascript\napp.setAppUserModelId('poi');\n```\n\nAdd I added a shortcut linked to `C:\\Users\\taroxd\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\electron-prebuilt\\dist\\electron.exe D:\\poi` to my start menu.\n\nBut it did not work. Have I done something wrong? Do I have to make a clone of electron to run my app, instead of using the globally installed electron?\n\nFYI, even if I do not set Application User Model ID, `Electron` will appear in `Show notifications from these apps` on Windows 10 Build 10240.\n"
