    "created_at": "2016-01-12T05:12:04Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-01-12T05:12:04Z",
    "body": "On Windows 8 to show notification for your app, you have to package your app as an independent app and install it in `%ProgramFiles%`, and then add a shortcut for it in start menu. I think Windows 10 is making things closer with Windows 8.\n\nAnyway the change is on Windows's side, there is nothing we can do except for following exactly [what Microsoft's docs requires](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/windows.ui.notifications.toastnotificationmanager.aspx).\n"
  },
